helm (0.4.0-1) trusty; urgency=low

  * Fixed a crash that would sometimes happen on startup in plugin version.
  * Midi input is marked "Helm" instead of "JUCE: Midi Input"
  * Fixed loading back parameters from DAW project.
  * Reenabled Mod Wheel input.
  * Pitch Wheel now changes pitch by default through "Pitch Bend" range knob.

